  <!-- EN: eltex dagger -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexDagger.label>靈質匕首</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexDagger.label>
  <!-- EN: A medieval dagger threaded with psychic focusing materials. While it enhances the wielder’s psychic sensitivity and neural heat dissipation, it also serves as an excellent melee weapon, as it follows the same idea as any other knife: A handle for holding and a sharp edge for cutting. -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexDagger.description>一把由靈能材料覆蓋的中世紀匕首。它特殊的材料增加了佩戴者的心靈敏感度，並且能夠更快地驅散心靈熵，同時也是一把趁手武器，因為根本的理念從未改變過：一個握把和連接在上面的鋒利的鋒利刀刃。</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexDagger.description>
  <!-- EN: handle -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexDagger.tools.handle.label>柄</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexDagger.tools.handle.label>
  <!-- EN: blade -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexDagger.tools.blade.label>刀刃</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexDagger.tools.blade.label>
  <!-- EN: point -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexDagger.tools.point.label>刀尖</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexDagger.tools.point.label>
  
  <!-- EN: eltex mace -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexMace.label>靈質釘錘</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexMace.label>
  <!-- EN: A medieval mace threaded with psychic focusing materials. While it enhances the wielder’s psychic sensitivity and neural heat dissipation, it also serves as an excellent melee weapon, engineered for efficient swinging and deadly impacts. -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexMace.description>一把由靈能材料覆蓋的中世紀釘錘。它特殊的材料增加了佩戴者的心靈敏感度，並且能夠更快地驅散心靈熵，同時也是一把趁手武器，在揮舞和殺傷上有特別的設計。</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexMace.description>
  <!-- EN: handle -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexMace.tools.handle.label>錘柄</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexMace.tools.handle.label>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexMace.tools.head.label>錘頭</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexMace.tools.head.label>
  
  <!-- EN: eltex sword -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexSword.label>靈質短劍</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexSword.label>
  <!-- EN: A medieval sword threaded with psychic focusing materials. While it enhances the wielder’s psychic sensitivity and neural heat dissipation, it also serves as an excellent melee weapon. Good for stabbing or slashing. It's light and nimble, which sometimes lets it beat bigger, heavier weapons. -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexSword.description>一把由靈能材料覆蓋的中世紀短劍。它特殊的材料增加了佩戴者的心靈敏感度，並且能夠更快地驅散心靈熵，同時也是一把趁手武器，劈砍或戳刺都非常有效。它輕巧靈活，這讓它有時候能擊敗更加巨大和沉重的武器。</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexSword.description>
  <!-- EN: handle -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexSword.tools.handle.label>劍柄</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexSword.tools.handle.label>
  <!-- EN: point -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexSword.tools.point.label>劍頭</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexSword.tools.point.label>
  <!-- EN: edge -->
  <VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexSword.tools.edge.label>劍刃</VPE_MeleeWeapon_EltexSword.tools.edge.label>
  
</LanguageData>